WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.470
Let's get started on using the cat command.

2
00:00:03.470 --> 00:00:05.525
To create the test1 file, type:

3
00:00:05.525 --> 00:00:10.390
"cat > test1" and press the Enter key.

4
00:00:10.390 --> 00:00:15.445
Type the sentence, "This is Sample File1", and press the Enter key,

5
00:00:15.445 --> 00:00:18.430
and press Ctrl+D to save the file.

6
00:00:18.430 --> 00:00:20.645
To create the test2 file, type:

7
00:00:20.645 --> 00:00:25.520
"cat > test2" and press the Enter key.

8
00:00:25.520 --> 00:00:30.425
Type the sentence, "This is Sample File2", and press the Enter key,

9
00:00:30.425 --> 00:00:33.475
and press Ctrl+D to save the file.

10
00:00:33.475 --> 00:00:36.000
To create the test3 file, type:

11
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.530
"cat > test3" and press the Enter key.

12
00:00:40.530 --> 00:00:44.060
Type the sentence, "This is Sample File3",

13
00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:50.560
and press the Enter key, and press Ctrl+D to save the file.

14
00:00:50.560 --> 00:00:57.325
To combine the files test1 and test2 into the file newtest, type:

15
00:00:57.325 --> 00:01:12.030
"cat test1 test2 > newtest",

16
00:01:12.030 --> 00:01:14.225
and press the Enter key.

17
00:01:14.225 --> 00:01:17.000
To view the newtest file, type:

18
00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:25.395
"cat newtest", and press the Enter key.

19
00:01:25.395 --> 00:01:29.935
The file newtest is displayed at the command prompt.

20
00:01:29.935 --> 00:01:33.555
To append a file to the end of newtest file, type:

21
00:01:33.555 --> 00:01:41.575
"cat test3 >> newtest",

22
00:01:42.975 --> 00:01:45.105
and press the Enter key.

23
00:01:45.105 --> 00:01:53.860
To view the newtest file, type: "cat newtest", and press the Enter key.

24
00:01:53.860 --> 00:01:57.345
The file newtest is displayed at the command prompt.

25
00:01:57.345 --> 00:01:59.370
To append the newtest file, type:

26
00:01:59.370 --> 00:02:07.170
"cat >> newtest",

27
00:02:07.170 --> 00:02:11.320
and press the Enter key.

28
00:02:11.320 --> 00:02:16.650
Type the sentence, "The Sample File3 is appended with another line",

29
00:02:16.650 --> 00:02:20.340
and press the Enter key, and press Ctrl+D.

30
00:02:20.340 --> 00:02:23.405
You will return to the command prompt.

31
00:02:23.405 --> 00:02:25.595
At the command prompt, type:

32
00:02:25.595 --> 00:02:33.405
"cat newtest", and press the Enter key.

33
00:02:33.405 --> 00:02:36.550
The newtest file is displayed.